metadata.name: The Elephant King
metadata.description:
There are shadows in the jungle of Goa Gajah. The thousand stares which doesn't creep but they are watching, very carefully. They protect their territory and isn't very keen of the human outsiders. Some of the settlements nearby worships them like the God Barong, and those Elephant deity shared powers so the village people able to accomplish wonders.
